<h4 id="yoclk--labview-controls">YOCLK &amp; LabVIEW Controls</h4>

<p>The lock operates based on an oscillating clock called ‚ÄúYOCLK‚Äù. The schematics of the lock as well as a video can be found <a href="/2014/01/28/yoclk/">here</a>. A LabVIEW program was created to be able to control and unlock the Lock Box called <a href="/2014/04/17/locktest-vi/">LockTest.vi</a>.</p>
